{"title":"飞翔的旋律——献给中国第一支舰载直升机部队（图片）","authors":["黄彩虹"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":7,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔的旋律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给中国第一支舰载直升机部队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄彩虹／摄影并配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海是你驰骋的舞台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空是你翱翔的疆场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次穿云破雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少回逐浪追星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当初羽翼未丰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今展翅腾空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天凭你挥洒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海任你叱咤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广袤天幕中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你舞动璀璨夺目的彩练。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫夜海上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你弹奏永久和平的旋律。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}